OL,6,FThe Victorian tramway to pier is not
OL,7,Fset to reopen until after Easter
OL,8,Ffollowing "extensive damage" caused by
OL,9,Fa fire last month.
OL,11,FSaltburn Cliff Lift suffered serious
OL,12,Finternal damage to the building and
OL,13,Foperating equipment, and in particular
OL,14,Fthe electrical pump room.
