OL,6,FAt the time, Redcar and Cleveland
OL,7,FCouncil said "extensive damage" had
OL,8,Fbeen caused to the Grade II-listed
OL,9,Fstructure. No one was injured.
OL,11,FThe Saltburn Cliff Lift, which is the
OL,12,Foldest water-balanced funicular in the
OL,13,FUK and the second oldest in the world,
OL,14,Fhad been closed at the time of the
OL,15,Ffire for winter maintenance.
OL,17,FThe cause of the blaze is said to be
OL,18,Felectrical.
