OL,3,C'Extensive' damage means historic
OL,4,Ctramway will not reopen for Easter
OL,6,FCllr Carrie Richardson, deputy leader
OL,7,Fof Redcar and Cleveland Council said:
OL,8,F"We regret that damage caused by a
OL,9,Fmajor fire to the much-loved and
OL,10,Fhugely popular Saltburn Tramway is
OL,11,Fextensive with serious internal damage
OL,12,Fto the building and operating
OL,13,Fequipment, especially the electrical
OL,14,Fpump room.
OL,16,F"A full rewire will be needed along
OL,17,Fwith careful restoration of this Grade-
OL,18,Flisted structure. Our teams are
OL,19,Fcontinuing to work hard on a plan to
OL,20,Fmake sure the Tramway reopens as soon
OL,21,Fas possible."
