OL,6,FShe said the work would likely "take
OL,7,Fsome time" and no date could be given
OL,8,Ffor the reopening.
OL,10,F"We look forward to reopening the
OL,11,Ficonic tramway when it is restored to
OL,12,Fits full glory and ready for future
OL,13,Fgenerations to enjoy," Cllr Richardson
OL,14,Fcontinued.
OL,16,F"We will continue to keep our
OL,17,Fresidents and visitors informed."
